  "text": "Historically, transcriptional reporter assays have facilitated the delineation of major signaling pathways. In particular, β-catenin-dependent luciferase-or GFP-based transcriptional reporters have been instrumental in elucidating the molecular mechanisms of the canonical Wnt/β-catenin pathway [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
